20:01.575 --> 20:02.410
[reporters clamor]

20:02.493 --> 20:05.621
-That's all I have to say. Thank you.
-[woman] Sir, we have one more...

20:05.705 --> 20:07.373
[woman on phone]<i> Ellenville Diner.</i>

20:07.456 --> 20:10.042
