20:10.126 --> 20:12.336
<i>-</i>[woman] <i>Why? What happened?</i>
-I gotta go back.

20:12.420 --> 20:14.839
[woman] <i>Where? Long Island, for Shannan?</i>

20:14.922 --> 20:18.259
Yeah, the police station,
they found bodies.

20:18.342 --> 20:19.885
[woman]<i> Oh, God. Do the girls know?</i>

20:19.969 --> 20:21.804
