22:11.288 --> 22:13.374
-I know it was a long drive--
-Are any of them her?

22:13.874 --> 22:15.626
[Dormer sighs] It appears not.

22:16.293 --> 22:18.671
-[sighs in relief]
-[Dormer] But we are working a grid

22:18.754 --> 22:19.797
as we speak.

22:19.880 --> 22:22.800
Tomorrow morning
we begin the aerial searches, first thing.

22:22.883 --> 22:26.220
That's assuming she's...
You're searching everywhere, right?

22:26.303 --> 22:27.680
Mm-hmm. Mm-hmm.

22:29.932 --> 22:33.561
I wanted to ask you some questions
about Shannan, if that's okay.

22:33.644 --> 22:37.648
Is there anything that you can tell me
about the men in Shannan's life?

22:38.107 --> 22:40.609
She has a boyfriend, Alex Diaz.

22:41.193 --> 22:43.153
Anybody else we should be looking at?

22:43.237 --> 22:45.155
A driver. Pak. Michael Pak.

22:45.656 --> 22:46.782
What about the doctor?

22:47.867 --> 22:49.410
[Dormer] What doctor?

22:49.493 --> 22:52.079
He called me
the morning after she went missing.

22:52.538 --> 22:54.415
He said he saw her and he helped her.

22:54.498 --> 22:56.292
He runs a home for wayward girls.

22:57.001 --> 22:58.002
What about her jacket?

22:58.085 --> 23:00.254
We have the jacket and it's being tested.

23:03.883 --> 23:05.843
Can you recall this doctor's name?

23:07.303 --> 23:09.138
[quietly] Fuck. Oh.

23:09.805 --> 23:11.682
Harper? Haskell?

23:11.765 --> 23:14.435
-It's okay. It's okay. It's okay.
-I don't remember.

23:15.769 --> 23:19.189
[Dormer] Mrs. Gilbert, there's a lot
we don't know at the moment.

23:20.316 --> 23:22.818
Which is why it's really important

23:23.736 --> 23:25.404
that you don't talk to the media.

23:25.988 --> 23:27.031
Let us handle that.

23:28.032 --> 23:30.492
One wrong word,
and they'll make a meal out of it.

23:30.576 --> 23:32.161
It's in your best interest.

23:33.120 --> 23:34.038
Sharon's, too.

23:35.372 --> 23:36.373
It's "Shannan."

23:37.207 --> 23:40.127
<i>The beautiful beaches</i>
<i>of Long Island, New York</i>

23:40.210 --> 23:42.671
<i>have become the latest backdrop</i>

23:42.755 --> 23:44.089
<i>in a murder mystery.</i>

23:44.173 --> 23:46.800
<i>The victims were engaged</i>
<i>in a high-risk business,</i>

23:46.884 --> 23:51.347
<i>and these homicides appear to us</i>
<i>to be directly related to that business.</i>

23:51.430 --> 23:54.183
[news reporter] <i>The Medical Examiner</i>
<i>determined the cause of death</i>

23:54.266 --> 23:56.685
<i>for the four women to be strangulation.</i>

23:56.769 --> 23:58.812
<i>Each body meticulously placed in bur--</i>

23:58.896 --> 24:00.564
[male reporter]
<i>24-year-old Shannan Gilbert,</i>

24:00.648 --> 24:02.107
<i>a prostitute from Jersey--</i>

24:02.191 --> 24:03.150
[turns TV off]

24:05.527 --> 24:07.738
