my daughter a prostitute again!

29:05.994 --> 29:08.789
[man laughing]

29:08.872 --> 29:09.706
[door bangs shut]

29:09.790 --> 29:11.625
[keyboard clacking]

29:11.708 --> 29:15.045
Okay, tell them we'll do the vigil,
but we want to meet them first.

29:15.128 --> 29:18.090
-And make sure everybody comes.
-What are you wearing?

29:23.011 --> 29:25.764
[keyboard clacking]

29:37.317 --> 29:40.487
[beeping]

29:40.570 --> 29:42.948
It's a long way to Oak Beach.

29:44.116 --> 29:46.827
-What were you guys talking about?
-[Pak] I don't know. I...

29:48.787 --> 29:49.788
work.

29:51.248 --> 29:52.249
The weather...

29:55.002 --> 29:56.753
Her and her boyfriend sneaking Taco Bell

29:56.837 --> 29:59.256
in the new Freddy movie
over at the Hudson Mall.

30:01.383 --> 30:03.635
Did she say anything
about going to visit her mom?

30:04.303 --> 30:06.054
[beeping continues]

30:06.722 --> 30:08.307
[laughs]

30:08.765 --> 30:10.809
Wait. Are you serious?

30:11.476 --> 30:14.938
[beeping continues]

30:15.022 --> 30:17.024
Do you know anything about her mom?

30:20.819 --> 30:23.739
Oh, my God. These women are so pathetic.

30:24.573 --> 30:25.991
The less we say, the better.

30:26.074 --> 30:28.535
We don't need them knowing
our personal business.

30:30.287 --> 30:31.288
What's that for?

30:31.371 --> 30:33.123
My notebook. I'm gonna take notes.

30:34.750 --> 30:35.584
[Mari sighs]

30:39.755 --> 30:41.256
Maybe we should go around?

30:42.382 --> 30:46.345
I'm Missy. I drove in from Connecticut
for my sister, Maureen.

30:47.304 --> 30:49.473
It's so good
to finally meet all of you in person.

30:50.682 --> 30:51.600
Mom.

30:53.935 --> 30:54.936
Say something.

30:59.191 --> 31:00.067
Uh, Lorraine.

31:01.568 --> 31:03.362
My daughter's Megan.

31:06.490 --> 31:08.700
I sold my TV to be here from Maine,

31:08.784 --> 31:11.495
so I have the cash to stay here
until the vigil.

31:12.829 --> 31:14.039
I'm Lynn.

31:15.582 --> 31:18.210
My daughter is Melissa.

31:19.169 --> 31:21.421
This is my other daughter, Amanda.

31:21.505 --> 31:23.048
We came here from Buffalo.

31:24.424 --> 31:25.258
[horn honks]

31:27.886 --> 31:29.262
[Lorraine] Oh. Kim is here.

31:32.808 --> 31:35.060
-[door opens]
-[Kim] Sorry, I'm late, y'all.

31:36.019 --> 31:38.230
[Missy] We were just going around
introducing ourselves.

31:38.313 --> 31:40.565
Where we're from, who we've lost.

31:40.649 --> 31:41.650
Okay. Kim...

31:42.484 --> 31:44.403
North Carolina. Um...

31:44.486 --> 31:46.530
I like Rocky Road ice cream

31:46.613 --> 31:48.573
and long walks on the beach,

31:48.657 --> 31:50.033
and my sister was Amber.

31:50.617 --> 31:51.451
[sniffs]

31:53.912 --> 31:54.913
Did I miss anything?

31:57.207 --> 32:00.377
[Pak over recording, laughing]
<i>Wait. Are you serious?</i>

32:01.002 --> 32:03.088
<i>Do you know anything about her mom?</i>

32:03.797 --> 32:05.715
<i>'Cause she's a real piece of work.</i>

32:06.716 --> 32:09.302
<i>Yeah, abandoned her own daughter</i>
<i>when she was just a kid.</i>

32:10.887 --> 32:13.557
<i>Shannan was in and out of foster homes</i>
<i>her whole life.</i>

32:14.516 --> 32:16.810
<i>All her mom is good for</i>
<i>is taking her money.</i>

32:18.645 --> 32:21.064
<i>Doesn't even care how Shannan made it.</i>

32:22.482 --> 32:24.734
<i>Just as long as she shared the wealth.</i>

32:26.278 --> 32:28.238
[Lorraine]
My daughter had three cellphones.

32:28.905 --> 32:30.740
[Lynn]
My daughter had three cellphones.

32:30.824 --> 32:34.703
She was working on the... Craigslist.

32:34.786 --> 32:36.538
[Missy] Yes, so did Maureen.

32:36.621 --> 32:38.081
[Lynn] So did Melissa.

32:38.165 --> 32:40.584
They all did.
That's why they're all so the same,

32:40.667 --> 32:42.711
because online,
you can practically go shopping.

32:42.794 --> 32:44.963
[Lorraine] Sooner or later,
they're gonna get this guy.

32:45.046 --> 32:46.298
There's gotta be some...

32:46.798 --> 32:48.508
computer trace they can do.

32:48.592 --> 32:50.552
[Kim]. Mm-mm. They don't get you on email.

32:50.635 --> 32:52.471
You post a number, then they call.

32:52.554 --> 32:56.224
Which is untraceable
because the girls work on burner phones.

32:56.308 --> 32:58.059
Look at you, knowing your shit.

32:58.727 --> 33:01.229
They think they're all drug addicts.

33:01.313 --> 33:04.232
-Melissa wasn't even into drugs.
-Neither was Maureen.

33:04.316 --> 33:05.192
She drank.

33:05.275 --> 33:08.153
