whether you want to believe it or not.

33:19.122 --> 33:20.457
[Lorraine sighs]

33:20.540 --> 33:23.210
They told me
Megan was where she wants to be.

33:24.044 --> 33:24.878
That, uh...

33:26.880 --> 33:28.173
