34:08.213 --> 34:10.549
What about our girls?
Who's talking about them?

34:11.383 --> 34:15.095
And when they do,
it's "prostitute," "hooker,"

34:15.512 --> 34:17.514
"sex worker," "escort."

34:18.056 --> 34:20.517
Never "friend," "sister,"

34:21.268 --> 34:22.477
"mother," "daughter."

34:23.812 --> 34:24.854
They don't care.

34:25.605 --> 34:26.731
They blame them.

34:28.358 --> 34:30.694
And it's our job, as mothers,

34:31.194 --> 34:32.487
and sisters,

34:33.363 --> 34:35.532
to make sure these girls
are not forgotten.

34:37.200 --> 34:38.827
So, should we wait on the vigil?

34:39.661 --> 34:42.455
No, we're doing the vigil.
We're going to Oak Beach,

34:43.039 --> 34:44.958
to their front fucking yard.

35:10.942 --> 35:12.360
